# Changelog

All notable changes to this project will be documented in this file.

The format is based on [Keep a Changelog](https://keepachangelog.com/en/1.1.0/),
and this project adheres to [Semantic Versioning](https://semver.org/spec/v2.0.0.html).

## [0.1.1] - 2024-09-04

## Added

- Documented the usage of `.env` files to store cognito configuration credentials.

## Fixed

- Bug related to the accidental activation of password togglers instead of submitting the form.

## [0.1.0] - 2024-09-04

## Added

- `getSession` public method.

## [0.0.5] - 2024-09-03

### Fixed

- Fixed incorrect error on ResetPassword flow. Success wouldn't ocurr even if it should.
- Fixed hide/show password buttons triggering form submit.

### Changed

- TailwindCSS Forms plugin only processes classes. Won't enforce global styles.
- Applied TailwindCSS Forms classses to input fields.

## [0.0.3] - 2024-08-26

### Changed

- Added preprocessing step for tailwindcss styles.

## [0.0.2] - 2024-08-26

### Changed

- Location of css styles file to fix broken behaviour.

## [0.0.1] - 2024-08-26

### Added

- This CHANGELOG file to keep track of changes.
- Minor documentation of library usage.
- Svelte components for major authentication methods and actions.
- Cognito's implementation through the authstore.
